{"tid":2189194,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"維尼帝真係千古一帝 必名留青史","createTime":"2020-09-04T16:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T17:06:48.000Z","uid":36134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"85e2ba025ccec1bfcdddd261d0eb8f43ff48f2ad","tid":2189194,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:59:24.000Z","msg":"西北集中管理新疆維吾爾族人<br />\n西南對抗印藏聯軍<br />\n南方鎮壓香港反對勢力<br />\n對北在全面清除蒙古落後文化 對落後反對勢力予以痛擊<br />\n對台 全力準備武統<br />\n<br />\n對日逐步走向不和<br />\n對歐 大展威權主義 震懾歐洲各國<br />\n對美展開史無前例既大對抗 脫離美國建立既世界體系<br />\n<br />\n此等偉業 我只想引用古詩歌中的一句形容<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">力拔山兮氣蓋世</span></span><br />\n真乃<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">中華霸王</span></span>"},{"pid":"c42677811ca5986e90108f63d5e382e119f91344","tid":2189194,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706f084a17380148a8d364b0e36e145a75abb8f7","tid":2189194,"uid":342557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"對外就口水軍，對內就揼水落重軍，中華第一懦夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2a934be9165e5359f05316ffc7b351ac6f0f4d","tid":2189194,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}